<br>
The reason i even went was i liked the raid leader and we always had a good time (translated.. we always kicked ass).<br>
<br>
Now that i have the opportunity to go again on an alt, i'll be darned if it is with someone who says he will just take the best piece of loot for himself.<br>
<br>
I was thinking about this the other day.. and in spite of not wanting to lead a raid myself.. i might just do that.. and noone gets to call any loot.. everything droppable is rolled on by all classes.<br>
<br>
The book is pally only but everything else is up for grabs.. i always thought that was a fair formula.. but got beat down a lot just for voicing my opinion.  Well, this raid was POSTED to Rants and Flames.. so too bad!<br>
